summary: In my twelve years of professional expertise in the Croatian Embassy in The Hague I performed senior administrative and senior assistance functions. I was in charge of many different managerial, organisational and technical tasks, supporting personnel at the Embassy. As PA to the Ambassador I was responsible for professional and private arrangements of four Croatian Ambassadors. I organised and shadowed every aspect of their work, guided them throughout their appointments, assisted them in establishing their professional and social network and in maintaining contact and communication with Diplomatic Missions, International Organizations, Dutch government officials and institutions. I planned and organised VIP visits, receptions, and other business, social and cultural events. I belong in a vibrant, international work atmosphere where I switch from language to language, multi-task and serve as a link between different cultures and mentalities. I genuinely like to care for others. I am highly responsible, adaptable, flexible, open to criticism and always ready to make an extra effort to create a working atmosphere of understanding and harmony.
